### Comment POST

@LastId = {{comments.response.body.$.data.rows[0].id}}
POST http://{{HOST}}/api/comments
content-type: application/json

{
  "id": {{LastId}},
  "author": "sobird",
  "content": "评论内容1 {{$guid}}",
  "email": "sobird@126.com"
}